item.title: SeaMeet Release History
item.description: 11/21/2024 # New Features and Improvements # Updated the SeaMeet landing page version Improved notifications for successful and failed Google Meet invitations Adjusted meeting status color indicators in the meeting list Bugfix # Resolved an issue where users who joined a meeting early could not pre-invite the bot via the extension Fixed an issue where users who joined late, after the bot had exited, could not reinvite the bot 11/14/2024 # New Features and Improvements # Improved the retry mechanism for bot rejoining meetings Resolved issues with the extension’s status checks Enhanced the stability of bot meeting recording termination 11/7/2024 # Bugfix # Fixed issues with data masking for users with canceled paid plans during error masking scenarios Adjusted the extension’s method for retrieving meeting IDs 10/31/2024 # New Features and Improvements # Added a light theme option.
